name: Ars Longa Vita Brevis - Art is Long Life is Short - Sanat uzun, Hayat kısa
description: Latin:Ars longa, vita brevis, occasio praeceps, experimentum periculosum, iudicium difficile.Eng:Art is long, life is short, opportunity fleeting, experience misleading, judgement difficult.Turkish:Sanat uzun, hayat kısa, fırsat kaçıcı, deneyim aldatıcı, karar zor.
